g.text: Following the release of his Music For Clouds LP, Voiski presents Sick Parrots, a compilation of 13 forgotten items, aborted projects,
alternative versions and exclusive tracks. Thirteen Impossible pieces to question the notion of releasability of a track, thus attempting to
enlighten about the making of a record. A bundle of artist indecisions genuinely gathered on a CD coming out in June on Voiski's SUPER 95.
